WEBVTT

01:39.370 --> 01:43.940
[Road to Success]

02:05.640 --> 02:06.430
Coach.

02:09.080 --> 02:10.810
I really can't hold on anymore.

02:12.530 --> 02:13.630
Pain

02:14.000 --> 02:15.470
is the price of growth.

02:32.280 --> 02:35.740
[Episode 13]

02:35.910 --> 02:36.910
Anyway,

02:37.079 --> 02:39.210
we've always been the abandoned ones.

02:39.750 --> 02:41.310
We're used to it.

02:42.000 --> 02:42.870
Ms. Lin,

02:44.079 --> 02:45.880
are we still training tomorrow?

02:58.030 --> 02:58.840
Never mind.

02:59.000 --> 03:00.200
Pretend I didn't ask.

03:21.480 --> 03:25.340
[Sports Equipment Room]

03:24.360 --> 03:25.470
Goodbye, Ms. Lin.

03:25.490 --> 03:26.300
Goodbye.

03:25.890 --> 03:33.300
[Sports Equipment Room]

03:34.150 --> 03:35.680
Surprise!

03:37.840 --> 03:38.730
Smells good.

03:42.800 --> 03:44.280
You go first. You go first.

03:48.630 --> 03:49.430
Is anyone here, Lu?

03:49.430 --> 03:50.560
No.

03:52.240 --> 03:53.740
I'll go first.

03:54.560 --> 03:56.590
Ms. Lin, give me your bag.

03:56.590 --> 03:58.079
Be careful. Be careful.

03:59.120 --> 04:00.910
-Boss.
-I can do it.

04:01.470 --> 04:02.280
Here you go.

04:04.030 --> 04:05.310
Help Ms. Lin.

04:07.630 --> 04:09.430
Be careful. Be careful.

04:10.910 --> 04:11.770
Give me the bag.

04:13.360 --> 04:14.630
Ms. Lin, this way.

04:27.310 --> 04:29.800
This is our secret base.

04:30.950 --> 04:32.440
Don't tell anyone.

04:32.830 --> 04:35.000
Or you'll be silenced.

04:35.000 --> 04:38.120
If you tell anyone,
you'll bear the consequences.

04:42.950 --> 04:43.720
Ms. Lin.

04:43.720 --> 04:44.830
-Please.
-Please.

04:53.270 --> 04:54.120
Is there anything I like?

04:54.120 --> 04:56.630
-Rice cakes.
-We have rice cakes?

04:57.480 --> 04:58.159
Ms. Lin.

04:59.310 --> 05:01.440
Your favorite, sweet and sour flavor.

05:03.390 --> 05:05.310
Ms. Lin, here are duck intestines

05:05.310 --> 05:06.970
and chicken, your favorites.

05:07.040 --> 05:08.560
Give me this. This one.

05:12.360 --> 05:13.680
What's going on today?

05:14.510 --> 05:15.830
Did you find your conscience?

05:15.830 --> 05:16.710
Come on.

05:16.830 --> 05:18.760
Can't we just treat you to skewers?

05:21.430 --> 05:23.160
Is it because of Coach?

05:27.160 --> 05:28.560
We're used to it.

05:28.560 --> 05:29.270
Right?

05:29.920 --> 05:31.240
It's just like before.

05:35.870 --> 05:36.830
No.

05:36.830 --> 05:38.950
Each of us got a tracksuit

05:38.950 --> 05:40.800
that will last until graduation.

05:40.800 --> 05:42.870
It always comes down to the same thing—

05:42.870 --> 05:45.120
playing football doesn't have as much of
a future as working in a factory.

05:45.120 --> 05:47.120
Studying is a bit better
than working in a factory.

05:47.120 --> 05:48.270
Anyway,

05:49.480 --> 05:51.810
I guess all good things
must come to an end.

05:54.800 --> 05:57.400
I didn't expect you
to say something like that.

05:57.680 --> 05:59.680
I'm a bad student, not illiterate.

06:00.390 --> 06:01.720
Looks like milk helps.

06:02.480 --> 06:03.630
Ms. Lin,

06:03.630 --> 06:05.490
can you talk to Coach again?

06:05.750 --> 06:07.160
What's there to talk about?

06:07.160 --> 06:08.890
He can make any choice he wants.

06:09.160 --> 06:10.270
Coach isn't an idiot.

06:10.270 --> 06:11.630
No one would choose us.

06:13.600 --> 06:15.120
We'd better record

06:15.120 --> 06:16.120
our training for the next few days.

06:16.120 --> 06:17.800
So we can train by ourselves
after he leaves.

06:17.800 --> 06:19.250
Are you stupid, bro?

06:19.680 --> 06:22.210
What's the point
of training without a coach?

06:22.830 --> 06:23.510
True.

06:25.920 --> 06:27.360
Try this.

06:27.360 --> 06:28.160
Fish tofu?

06:30.190 --> 06:31.750
I've been looking for ages,

06:31.750 --> 06:33.550
and where's the squid I ordered?

06:40.430 --> 06:41.560
Ms. Lin,

06:41.560 --> 06:43.159
you've done enough.

06:43.680 --> 06:45.800
Even if Coach chooses another team,

06:45.800 --> 06:47.040
that's his choice.

06:47.480 --> 06:48.600
Anyway,

06:49.360 --> 06:51.090
thanks for everything lately.

06:56.680 --> 06:58.810
Ms. Lin, you don't need to feel guilty.

06:59.430 --> 07:00.480
We know exactly

07:00.480 --> 07:01.830
what we're capable of.

07:02.270 --> 07:04.240
Playing football won't make us money.

07:04.240 --> 07:05.360
And our grades

07:05.360 --> 07:07.490
are just as bad as our football skills.

07:08.240 --> 07:09.920
If we give up football now

07:10.360 --> 07:11.390
and study hard,

07:12.480 --> 07:15.000
we might barely make it into a college.

07:18.750 --> 07:20.610
Wait, why are these all spicy too?

07:21.000 --> 07:21.830
This is not spicy.

07:21.830 --> 07:22.360
This one.

07:22.600 --> 07:23.160
And these.

07:23.160 --> 07:23.680
Hand me a skewer

07:23.680 --> 07:24.680
of squid.

07:25.920 --> 07:27.270
-I forgot to order it.
-We didn't order it.

07:27.270 --> 07:28.430
Why do you guys

07:31.190 --> 07:32.750
play football?

07:34.000 --> 07:35.040
I've played since I was little.

07:35.040 --> 07:36.240
It's a habit, I guess.

07:36.550 --> 07:38.000
There's no reason.

07:38.000 --> 07:39.060
I just want to play.

07:39.600 --> 07:41.560
I used to play to prove it to my mom.

07:41.560 --> 07:43.390
Now I play to prove it to myself.

07:45.680 --> 07:46.480
I like it.

07:50.560 --> 07:51.120
Cool.

07:51.560 --> 07:52.680
Yeah.

07:59.750 --> 08:01.010
If you have the chance,

08:01.650 --> 08:03.710
will you guys keep playing football?

08:04.560 --> 08:06.270
This question is very important.

08:06.270 --> 08:08.270
Think clearly before you answer me.

08:19.600 --> 08:20.600
Ms. Lin,

08:21.600 --> 08:23.040
we really have nothing.

08:23.680 --> 08:25.480
Playing football is the only way

08:25.680 --> 08:27.360
we can prove ourselves.

08:38.669 --> 08:40.470
I'm going out for some fresh air.

08:40.789 --> 08:42.250
-I'll go too.
-I'll go too.

09:12.630 --> 09:14.570
Calling me back after work

09:14.840 --> 09:16.480
is really too much.

09:19.750 --> 09:21.350
I have an important question

09:21.550 --> 09:23.150
I'd like to discuss with you.

09:33.910 --> 09:35.320
Can you tell me

09:36.750 --> 09:37.670
why people

09:39.510 --> 09:41.000
play football?

09:46.440 --> 09:48.510
It's pointless for me to tell you.

09:50.390 --> 09:52.250
A person without their own answer

09:54.030 --> 09:56.360
cannot understand the answers of others.

10:29.600 --> 10:30.800
Watch my stuff for me.

10:30.960 --> 10:32.430
Call me in 90 minutes.

10:48.590 --> 10:50.110
♪ The night sky and starlight ♪

10:50.480 --> 10:55.280
♪ Secret words falling into my palm ♪

10:55.770 --> 10:57.150
♪ Unraveling the mystery ♪

10:57.810 --> 11:02.030
♪ It was you who gave me this brilliance ♪

11:02.870 --> 11:04.450
♪ Lasting memories ♪

11:05.190 --> 11:09.480
♪ The distance
that brings our dreams closer ♪

11:10.080 --> 11:11.400
♪ To run toward you ♪

11:11.730 --> 11:16.510
♪ I keep practicing with no turning back ♪

11:19.740 --> 11:21.430
♪ There's nothing to fear ♪

11:22.150 --> 11:23.680
♪ Because you're with me ♪

11:26.630 --> 11:28.090
♪ The light shimmers ♪

11:29.330 --> 11:30.620
♪ Brilliant as stars ♪

11:32.240 --> 11:33.300
♪ Running towards you ♪

11:34.260 --> 11:35.450
♪ I keep moving fearlessly ♪

11:39.300 --> 11:40.280
♪ Walk side by side ♪

11:41.110 --> 11:43.230
♪ Become ourselves ♪

11:45.260 --> 11:46.660
♪ Amid the storm ♪

11:47.260 --> 11:51.650
♪ As our breaths slowly intertwine ♪

11:50.000 --> 11:51.270
I'm so tired.

11:51.790 --> 11:53.270
Running is already so tiring.

11:52.070 --> 11:53.470
♪ Heartbeats alternating ♪

11:54.080 --> 11:55.720
Playing football will only be more tiring.

11:54.150 --> 11:58.740
♪ A tacit understanding
about to emerge ♪

11:57.240 --> 11:59.150
Then why do they play football?

11:59.490 --> 12:00.420
♪ The stars are shining ♪

12:01.130 --> 12:05.880
♪ Take my hand and run forward ♪

12:02.390 --> 12:04.520
If I don't even understand this,

12:04.800 --> 12:06.980
how can I lead them in football?

12:06.470 --> 12:07.390
♪ I am willing, for you ♪

12:08.280 --> 12:13.030
♪ To practice repeatedly like this ♪

12:16.320 --> 12:18.010
♪ There's nothing to fear ♪

12:18.730 --> 12:20.260
♪ Because you're with me ♪

12:20.840 --> 12:22.240
What is it exactly

12:22.410 --> 12:24.380
that makes them endure such exhaustion,

12:23.220 --> 12:24.680
♪ The light shimmers ♪

12:24.410 --> 12:26.640
yet persist in playing game after game?

12:25.920 --> 12:27.200
♪ Brilliant as stars ♪

12:28.830 --> 12:29.890
♪ Running towards you ♪

12:30.850 --> 12:31.910
♪ I keep moving fearlessly ♪

12:35.790 --> 12:38.440
What they pursue
with all their might on the pitch—

12:35.890 --> 12:36.760
♪ Walk side by side ♪

12:37.690 --> 12:39.610
♪ Become ourselves ♪

12:38.820 --> 12:40.460
what exactly is it?

12:53.160 --> 12:54.240
Could it be

12:54.550 --> 12:56.370
that pursuing beautiful things

12:56.670 --> 12:58.390
and pouring our passion into them

12:58.390 --> 13:00.550
is a natural instinct?

13:01.080 --> 13:03.140
With absolute love and desire,

13:03.510 --> 13:05.940
does it matter if there's a reason?

13:09.750 --> 13:10.750
I'll run with you.

13:28.800 --> 13:30.490
♪ Regaining courage ♪

13:31.200 --> 13:32.880
♪ Because you're with me ♪

13:35.680 --> 13:37.150
♪ Heartbeat's response ♪

13:38.380 --> 13:39.730
♪ Brilliant as stars ♪

14:01.600 --> 14:03.200
How long have I been running?

14:04.120 --> 14:06.650
If you only count the time
you ran by yourself,

14:07.510 --> 14:08.510
it's 41 minutes.

14:09.480 --> 14:11.510
Not even half the time of the match.

14:16.910 --> 14:17.870
So,

14:18.510 --> 14:20.080
do you have an answer now?

14:32.840 --> 14:34.240
My answer is

14:36.270 --> 14:38.800
that you don't need a reason
to play football.

14:38.870 --> 14:39.870
What matters is

14:41.720 --> 14:43.390
the courageous first step.

14:49.510 --> 14:50.750
Over the past month,

14:52.030 --> 14:54.670
too many unexpected things have happened.

14:56.000 --> 14:57.200
When I first got here,

14:57.550 --> 14:58.510
I thought there would be

14:58.510 --> 15:00.370
no more possibilities in my life.

15:04.960 --> 15:05.840
What about now?

15:11.670 --> 15:12.790
Now...

15:19.840 --> 15:21.840
Now I have so much I can't let go of—

15:24.150 --> 15:25.910
people and things.

15:44.080 --> 15:45.040
Anyway,

15:45.240 --> 15:47.370
we've always been the abandoned ones.

15:47.910 --> 15:49.670
We're used to it.

15:54.600 --> 15:55.870
Ms. Lin,

15:56.630 --> 15:58.140
we really have nothing.

15:58.600 --> 16:00.600
Playing football is the only way

16:00.600 --> 16:02.240
we can prove ourselves.

16:17.720 --> 16:19.920
I have always respected their choices.

16:22.320 --> 16:23.910
But I never thought

16:25.480 --> 16:28.000
that they had already made their choices.

16:30.030 --> 16:32.790
They just desperately
need someone to help them.

16:38.600 --> 16:40.730
I'm the one who should make the choice.

16:46.840 --> 16:48.550
To help or not to help?

16:56.790 --> 16:57.460
I'll help.

17:13.680 --> 17:14.550
Your legs are sore, right?

17:14.550 --> 17:15.200
Stop playing tough.

17:15.200 --> 17:15.720
Take a rest.

17:15.720 --> 17:16.480
No need.

17:16.829 --> 17:18.200
We're almost there.

17:19.829 --> 17:21.480
I mean you should stand aside for a while.

17:21.480 --> 17:22.589
Otherwise,
you'll block the people behind you.

17:22.589 --> 17:23.440
Like me.

17:41.360 --> 17:42.220
[Receive Money by QR Code]

17:50.580 --> 17:50.860
[Receive Money by QR Code]

18:02.070 --> 18:03.130
Hello, passenger.

18:12.400 --> 18:14.780
♪ Night slips through my fingers ♪

18:15.630 --> 18:19.470
♪ Embracing the coldness of wakefulness ♪

18:20.340 --> 18:22.170
♪ Whispering my thoughts alone ♪

18:22.700 --> 18:27.600
♪ Saying goodbye to the evening breeze
we met by chance ♪

18:28.190 --> 18:30.840
♪ Staying with the jasmine blossoms
until late spring ♪

18:31.510 --> 18:34.600
♪ Watching their elegance fade,
their fragrance disappear ♪

18:35.900 --> 18:38.610
♪ I once dreamed of beauty ♪

18:39.750 --> 18:41.550
Be careful. Don't drop me.

18:39.840 --> 18:43.700
♪ And I accept that
regrets may grow wild ♪

18:41.550 --> 18:43.070
I won't.

18:43.070 --> 18:45.510
Your Highness, the shining genius Wanxing.

18:44.380 --> 18:46.580
♪ Look, beneath the sunlight ♪

18:45.830 --> 18:47.830
You're making fun of me
at a time like this?

18:47.370 --> 18:51.290
♪ In the dancing specks of dust ♪

18:52.090 --> 18:54.850
♪ I'm grateful I never lost my sincerity ♪

18:55.030 --> 18:56.750
I'll walk by myself from here.

18:55.510 --> 18:59.280
♪ Or my gift for happiness ♪

18:57.000 --> 18:58.240
It's only a few steps.

19:00.180 --> 19:02.920
♪ Sharing my warmth with a passing rain ♪

19:03.660 --> 19:07.280
♪ Quietly feeling its journey ♪

19:08.710 --> 19:10.990
♪ Like a firefly vanishing in an instant ♪

19:20.890 --> 19:22.430
[Ming]

19:22.530 --> 19:23.460
[Extract Files]

19:23.740 --> 19:24.210
[Psychological Case Files] [Ming]

19:24.550 --> 19:27.120
[Enter Password]

19:27.260 --> 19:28.070
[Confirm]

19:28.090 --> 19:28.720
[Ming]

19:30.690 --> 19:31.040
[Ming]

19:31.510 --> 19:33.230
[Chat History]

19:33.880 --> 19:35.500
[Chat History with Ming]

19:35.920 --> 19:36.510
[If anything's bothering you,
you can always tell me.]

19:36.530 --> 19:36.940
[My major is psychology anyway.
At least I can talk to you]

19:36.960 --> 19:37.440
[And help you get to know
more about yourself.]

19:37.460 --> 19:37.880
[What do you mean?]

19:37.900 --> 19:40.530
[Then you can start
a hunger strike tomorrow]

19:40.560 --> 19:42.970
[Robots don't need to eat or drink anyway]

19:45.400 --> 19:46.480
Ming.

19:45.830 --> 19:46.600
[I hate you]

19:46.630 --> 19:47.200
[Before I knew it,
it was already New Year's.]

19:47.200 --> 19:47.900
[How was your day?]

19:47.400 --> 19:50.030
Maybe I couldn't help you,

19:50.480 --> 19:53.480
but I can't give up helping others.

20:00.510 --> 20:01.440
Good afternoon.

20:01.510 --> 20:02.590
-Ms. Lin.
-Ms. Lin.

20:02.590 --> 20:03.830
- Coach.
- Hello, Coach.

20:03.830 --> 20:04.830
Everyone is here.

20:05.070 --> 20:06.350
Ms. Lin is here.

20:06.880 --> 20:08.150
Move the tables.

20:08.310 --> 20:09.510
Move the tables to the middle.

20:09.510 --> 20:10.480
Ms. Lin.

20:11.070 --> 20:12.790
Hello, Ms. Lin. Hello, Coach.

20:19.830 --> 20:20.750
Ms. Lin,

20:20.750 --> 20:23.310
did you call us here today
to announce something?

20:23.310 --> 20:24.310
To be exact,

20:24.310 --> 20:26.840
there is a topic
I want to discuss with you all.

20:27.350 --> 20:29.340
About what you want to do.

20:29.370 --> 20:30.620
What do we want to do?

20:30.640 --> 20:32.430
What do we want to do?

20:32.430 --> 20:33.270
How should we talk about it?

20:33.270 --> 20:35.110
There are so many things we want to do.

20:35.110 --> 20:36.000
Are there?

20:36.000 --> 20:37.750
Of course. Too many to count.

20:37.750 --> 20:38.750
That's great.

20:39.110 --> 20:40.110
Pass the pens around.

20:40.110 --> 20:41.070
Okay.

20:53.480 --> 20:54.540
Thank you, Ms. Lin.

20:56.030 --> 20:57.960
Does everyone have a pen and paper?

20:58.110 --> 20:59.160
Next,

20:59.160 --> 21:00.880
on the paper in your hands,

21:00.880 --> 21:02.640
write down 100 things

21:02.640 --> 21:04.680
you want to do most in the future.

21:04.700 --> 21:06.850
-100 things?
-100 things?

21:07.510 --> 21:09.160
What if I don't want to write it?

21:09.160 --> 21:11.480
When I was in college,

21:11.480 --> 21:13.310
my professor
also made me do this exercise.

21:13.310 --> 21:15.440
I think it was quite meaningful to me.

21:15.460 --> 21:16.420
It's up to you.

21:39.900 --> 21:41.290
[Qi Liang: Slack off and do nothing]

21:42.510 --> 21:45.600
[Lin Lu: Buy a PS5;
become No.1 on the national server]

21:47.810 --> 21:49.800
[Feng Suo: Go to outer space;
buy a Benz; see aliens;]

21:49.830 --> 21:51.740
[go to Mars; make lots of money]

21:54.160 --> 21:54.780
[Chen Jianghe: Reach 100 stars in the game;
join the national team]

21:54.800 --> 21:55.440
[lead the national team to win the championship;
crush Cristiano Ronaldo in a friendly match]

21:55.470 --> 21:56.170
[invent a perpetual motion machine;
fly out of the Milky Way; tackle Qin Ao]

21:57.320 --> 21:57.670
[Fu Xinshu: Never get injured;]

21:57.700 --> 21:58.070
[have an unbreakable football;
get married]

21:58.090 --> 21:58.400
[to the girl I like; see snowy mountains;
go to a university]

21:58.420 --> 21:58.830
[with air-conditioned classrooms;
return to primitive life]

22:25.460 --> 22:26.870
Yu Ming.

22:26.890 --> 22:28.950
No peeking. Write your own wishes.

22:30.000 --> 22:31.240
Ms. Lin,

22:31.240 --> 22:32.840
I really have no more wishes.

22:33.270 --> 22:34.310
Think carefully.

22:35.830 --> 22:37.000
Ms. Lin,

22:37.000 --> 22:38.480
to be honest with you,

22:38.480 --> 22:40.310
we don't want to dampen your enthusiasm.

22:40.310 --> 22:41.310
We've had classes

22:41.310 --> 22:42.720
like this before.

22:42.970 --> 22:44.030
Isn't it just to help us

22:44.030 --> 22:45.510
find our life goals?

22:46.400 --> 22:47.660
Do you think it helped?

22:48.310 --> 22:49.590
Honestly,

22:49.590 --> 22:50.310
it didn't.

22:50.310 --> 22:52.160
My primary school teacher
asked me back then,

22:52.160 --> 22:54.110
"What is your dream?"

22:54.110 --> 22:54.750
I said,

22:54.750 --> 22:56.550
"I want to be a scientist."

22:56.550 --> 22:58.350
Do I look like one?

22:58.370 --> 22:59.900
-Not at all.
-You're right.

23:01.720 --> 23:04.110
The founder of humanistic psychology,

23:04.110 --> 23:06.840
Abraham Maslow, once said,

23:07.070 --> 23:08.830
"Knowing what one wants

23:08.830 --> 23:11.110
is not a normal thing.

23:11.110 --> 23:13.070
It is a rare and difficult

23:13.070 --> 23:15.270
psychological achievement to reach."

23:21.510 --> 23:23.680
Ms. Lin's quote

23:23.680 --> 23:25.030
was pretty classy.

23:26.000 --> 23:27.750
You impressed us again.

23:29.270 --> 23:30.510
Keep writing.

24:02.510 --> 24:03.160
Are you done?

24:03.160 --> 24:03.880
Yeah.

24:04.960 --> 24:06.270
I'm done, Ms. Lin.

24:06.270 --> 24:07.350
Done, Ms. Lin.

24:07.720 --> 24:08.830
Next,

24:08.830 --> 24:11.480
please delete 20 things from it

24:11.480 --> 24:14.030
that you think
you absolutely can't achieve.

24:15.750 --> 24:16.880
We worked so hard to write them,

24:16.880 --> 24:18.680
and you want us to cross them out?

24:24.550 --> 24:25.510
We'll do it.

24:31.850 --> 24:32.720
[Wen Chengye and Lin Lu; eat more;
sleep more; drink more; run more]

24:32.740 --> 24:33.930
[jump more; beat Dog Wen more]

24:35.180 --> 24:36.360
[I hope to rank
in the top 500 in the exam]

24:36.380 --> 24:37.540
[Own 10 Rolls-Royces]

24:39.460 --> 24:41.180
[I want to get into a good university]

24:41.440 --> 24:42.750
Don't cross this one out.

24:42.750 --> 24:43.960
It's not impossible.

24:45.440 --> 24:46.510
Then cross this out first.

24:46.510 --> 24:47.980
Cross out the time machine one too.

24:47.980 --> 24:49.170
[I want to take a time machine]

24:49.190 --> 24:50.260
[Win 10 million in the lottery]

24:52.340 --> 24:52.900
[Leave the solar system]

24:52.930 --> 24:53.800
[See aliens]

24:57.590 --> 24:58.720
Are you done crossing them out?

24:58.720 --> 24:59.830
-Yes.
-Yes.

24:59.830 --> 25:00.510
Yes.

25:00.510 --> 25:03.070
Next, please cross out 20 things

25:03.070 --> 25:05.590
that you think are less important.

25:05.590 --> 25:07.240
More crossing out?

25:07.240 --> 25:07.960
Come on.

25:07.960 --> 25:10.240
Then why did you make us write so much?

25:13.480 --> 25:14.510
Just do it.

25:21.700 --> 25:22.250
[Eat chicken nuggets; eat fried chicken;
drink Cola; drink Sprite]

25:22.270 --> 25:22.980
[Drink more water; eat fewer vegetables]

25:29.610 --> 25:30.690
[Eat Ginger Duck]

25:30.710 --> 25:31.770
[Go to the beach to watch the sunset]

25:33.480 --> 25:34.350
Done, Ms. Lin.

25:35.270 --> 25:36.310
What about the others?

25:36.310 --> 25:37.640
-Done.
-Done, Ms. Lin.

25:37.640 --> 25:38.480
Almost done.

25:39.030 --> 25:40.010
Next,

25:40.480 --> 25:41.900
cross out 20 more.

25:42.070 --> 25:42.720
What?

25:42.720 --> 25:44.030
What, Ms. Lin?

25:44.030 --> 25:46.240
Do you know how hard it was
to think of these?

25:46.240 --> 25:48.660
Ms. Lin, are you messing with us?

25:49.270 --> 25:50.670
I'm not messing with you.

25:50.720 --> 25:51.690
Trust me.

25:51.790 --> 25:53.640
It's not like you can't achieve

25:53.640 --> 25:55.480
or get the things you crossed out

25:55.480 --> 25:56.720
in the future.

25:56.720 --> 25:59.030
It's just that for now,

25:59.030 --> 26:00.270
you don't need them as much.

26:00.270 --> 26:02.260
So they have to leave temporarily.

26:02.400 --> 26:04.070
You just need to tell us now

26:04.070 --> 26:05.310
how many things we should keep.

26:05.310 --> 26:06.700
-Yeah.
-Yeah.

26:08.480 --> 26:09.160
Five.

26:10.510 --> 26:11.440
Why five?

26:12.200 --> 26:14.000
Because psychologists have said

26:14.000 --> 26:15.760
that people can process at most

26:15.790 --> 26:17.790
5 to 7 choices at the same time.

26:17.790 --> 26:20.400
Otherwise, choice overload will occur.

26:20.400 --> 26:21.510
Then I'll keep 7.

26:37.850 --> 26:38.410
[Take a photo with Cristiano Ronaldo]

26:38.440 --> 26:39.480
[Become a muscular man]

26:41.820 --> 26:46.710
[Make 1 million]

26:52.590 --> 26:55.200
[Go to Jay Chou's concert]

26:57.820 --> 27:00.100
[Go to Jay Chou's concert]

27:01.570 --> 27:03.370
[Watch a World Cup final]

27:08.170 --> 27:10.500
[Watch a World Cup final]

27:12.640 --> 27:14.190
[Watch a World Cup final]

27:22.350 --> 27:24.480
[I want to get into a good university]

27:31.640 --> 27:32.550
Done.

27:32.550 --> 27:33.880
Done.

27:33.880 --> 27:34.920
Finally,

27:35.880 --> 27:37.870
cross out 4 more things

27:38.030 --> 27:38.790
and only keep one.

27:38.790 --> 27:40.270
More, Ms. Lin?

27:40.270 --> 27:41.350
I really can't choose anymore.

27:41.350 --> 27:42.720
Just punch me.

27:48.310 --> 27:49.750
Why must we listen to you

27:49.750 --> 27:50.750
and make this choice?

27:50.750 --> 27:52.310
Why can't we choose them all?

27:52.310 --> 27:53.720
-Is there only one path in life?
-Exactly.

27:53.720 --> 27:55.550
Why must we make a choice?

27:55.550 --> 27:57.410
It is indeed very uncomfortable.

28:03.550 --> 28:04.350
Indeed.

28:05.400 --> 28:07.330
There are so many beautiful things

28:08.070 --> 28:10.070
in this world that we can't let go of.

28:10.400 --> 28:13.310
In the process
of constantly analyzing your own heart,

28:13.310 --> 28:15.270
what is that thing buried deep inside—

28:15.270 --> 28:18.000
the thing you'd rather endure the pain
of giving up

28:18.000 --> 28:19.660
other things again and again,

28:21.310 --> 28:22.440
yet still hold on to?

28:24.000 --> 28:25.600
Everyone, think carefully.

29:46.320 --> 29:46.730
[I want to take a time machine]

29:46.480 --> 29:48.070
You have never disappointed me.

29:46.750 --> 29:47.150
[Make more friends]

29:47.170 --> 29:47.500
[The latest phone]

29:47.520 --> 29:48.010
[Get stronger and protect my classmates]

29:48.030 --> 29:48.530
[Go to a concert with Boss]

29:48.070 --> 29:49.400
Well done.

29:48.550 --> 29:49.020
[Be happy every day]

29:49.050 --> 29:49.570
[Travel abroad]

29:49.590 --> 29:50.030
[I hope my family stays healthy]

29:50.050 --> 29:50.510
[Become No.1 on the national server]

29:50.530 --> 29:50.860
[I hope to rank
in the top 500 in the exam]

29:50.930 --> 29:52.550
[Win the championship]

29:56.570 --> 29:57.340
[Win the championship with my bros]

29:57.390 --> 29:57.870
[Slack off and do nothing]

29:57.640 --> 29:59.510
Infinite stamina is just broken!

29:57.890 --> 29:58.300
[I hope I can use Flash]

29:58.330 --> 29:58.850
[Infinite stamina]

29:58.870 --> 30:00.990
[Enjoy every football match]

29:59.510 --> 30:01.750
This is my ultimate dream.

30:01.750 --> 30:02.880
Why did you write down
all kinds of wishes?

30:02.880 --> 30:03.830
Ms. Lin said that...

30:03.830 --> 30:05.240
You're going to save the world?

30:05.240 --> 30:06.510
Let's see what Zhi Hui wrote.

30:06.510 --> 30:09.240
"Win the championship with the guys."

30:07.310 --> 30:08.360
♪ Time's passing by ♪

30:09.240 --> 30:10.960
♪ Nothing remains ♪

30:09.240 --> 30:11.350
-Not bad, Zhi Hui.
-It's the same as mine.

30:11.350 --> 30:12.640
Let's see Fu's.

30:11.910 --> 30:14.800
♪ All the dreamers awake alone ♪

30:12.640 --> 30:14.750
"Win the football championship."

30:15.160 --> 30:16.830
As expected, everyone thinks alike.

30:15.490 --> 30:17.020
♪ Shadows above ♪

30:17.030 --> 30:18.240
Not bad, Fu.

30:17.910 --> 30:18.690
[Unlimited chicken legs]

30:17.980 --> 30:19.640
♪ Rain falls around ♪

30:18.720 --> 30:21.090
[I hope our team wins the championship]

30:20.270 --> 30:20.970
♪ In your arms ♪

30:21.880 --> 30:23.250
♪ We become one ♪

30:23.820 --> 30:25.360
♪ Through day and night ♪

30:25.270 --> 30:27.520
[Go to Europe
to watch Premier League matches]

30:25.790 --> 30:28.160
"Play football with my bros."

30:26.220 --> 30:28.590
♪ I can see you ♪

30:28.160 --> 30:29.830
Being sentimental again, huh?

30:29.560 --> 30:31.800
♪ In my eyes ♪

30:29.850 --> 30:30.210
[Get a perfect score
in the college entrance exam]

30:30.240 --> 30:30.690
[Climb mountains every day]

30:30.720 --> 30:32.200
[But what I want most in the end]

30:32.220 --> 30:34.100
[is to win a championship with the guys]

30:32.520 --> 30:33.970
♪ Just hold me tight ♪

30:34.810 --> 30:40.150
♪ Look into my soul so deeply ♪

30:39.630 --> 30:40.150
[Have a puppy]

30:40.180 --> 30:40.630
[Have a kitten]

30:40.690 --> 30:42.290
[Win the championship]

30:41.380 --> 30:42.780
♪ Rainbow sunlight ♪

30:43.520 --> 30:44.660
♪ Painful tears are gone ♪

30:45.170 --> 30:45.610
[Win the championship]

30:45.700 --> 30:46.070
[Grow to 2 meters tall]

30:45.840 --> 30:46.510
♪ Wonderful dreams ♪

30:46.090 --> 30:46.890
[Buy a genuine Bandai Gundam]

30:46.890 --> 30:49.910
[Win a championship]

30:47.590 --> 30:48.940
♪ Are so close to me ♪

30:47.830 --> 30:49.790
Qin Ao.

30:50.260 --> 30:51.150
♪ Memories fly ♪

30:52.040 --> 30:53.290
♪ Leave them all behind ♪

30:52.270 --> 30:53.070
Don't read it!

30:54.300 --> 30:59.900
♪ Just take my hand and stay with me ♪

30:55.340 --> 30:57.310
-Everyone has seen it anyway.
-What's the big deal?

30:57.310 --> 30:58.960
It doesn't matter if we read it or not.

30:58.960 --> 31:00.440
Didn't someone say

31:00.440 --> 31:03.170
not to ask him
for this kind of thing in the future?

31:04.480 --> 31:05.400
I just want to win the championship.

31:05.030 --> 31:06.710
♪ Rainbow sunlight ♪

31:05.400 --> 31:06.730
What's wrong with that?

31:07.310 --> 31:08.880
Even if it's wishful thinking,

31:07.720 --> 31:08.820
♪ Painful tears are gone ♪

31:09.490 --> 31:10.700
♪ Wonderful dreams ♪

31:09.510 --> 31:10.570
I still want to win.

31:11.240 --> 31:12.930
♪ Are so close to me ♪

31:13.920 --> 31:15.300
♪ Memories fly ♪

31:14.450 --> 31:16.000
What's wrong with wishful thinking?

31:16.000 --> 31:17.720
At least we dare to think.

31:16.240 --> 31:17.490
♪ Leave them all behind ♪

31:18.380 --> 31:21.880
♪ Just take my hand and stay with me ♪

31:22.470 --> 31:24.430
♪ Rainbow sunlight ♪

31:23.680 --> 31:25.270
Do you remember Leicester City F.C.?

31:24.780 --> 31:26.290
♪ Painful tears are gone ♪

31:26.950 --> 31:28.190
♪ Wonderful dreams ♪

31:27.480 --> 31:29.310
Leicester City F.C.?

31:28.740 --> 31:30.440
♪ Are so close to me ♪

31:29.610 --> 31:32.150
In the 2013–14 season, they were still
playing in the Championship.

31:31.350 --> 31:32.750
♪ Memories fly ♪

31:32.150 --> 31:35.000
In 2014–15,
they barely avoided relegation.

31:33.130 --> 31:34.750
♪ Leave them all behind ♪

31:35.000 --> 31:36.880
Then, in 2015–16,
they went on to win the title.

31:35.380 --> 31:42.320
♪ Just take my hand and stay with me ♪

31:37.790 --> 31:40.000
Bros, the Premier League title.

31:40.000 --> 31:41.800
If this isn't a miracle, what is?

31:42.400 --> 31:44.350
We even beat Lyujing International.

31:44.350 --> 31:45.240
Exactly.

31:45.240 --> 31:46.070
Since we beat Lyujing,

31:46.070 --> 31:47.550
we can advance to the group stage.

31:47.550 --> 31:49.480
The group stage is a double round-robin.

31:49.480 --> 31:50.960
If we get a good draw,

31:50.960 --> 31:52.310
we'll have a chance of qualifying.

31:52.310 --> 31:53.640
Since you say so,

31:53.640 --> 31:54.920
if we have better luck,

31:54.920 --> 31:56.320
we can reach the top four.

31:56.680 --> 31:58.310
-It's possible.
-We may be able to win the championship.

31:58.310 --> 31:59.830
But if Coach leaves,

32:00.400 --> 32:02.200
how can we win the championship?

32:08.030 --> 32:09.690
Coach hasn't left yet, has he?

32:11.000 --> 32:12.160
If there is no Coach,

32:12.640 --> 32:14.160
or even me,

32:15.200 --> 32:16.460
will you stop playing?

32:23.790 --> 32:26.250
Ms. Lin's question
is also what I want to ask.

32:27.960 --> 32:29.160
Without the two of us,

32:29.510 --> 32:31.000
would you stop playing?

32:40.480 --> 32:41.240
No.

32:45.400 --> 32:46.200
Without you,

32:46.790 --> 32:48.250
we're still going to play.

32:51.770 --> 32:54.030
Yes, and we want to win
the championship.

32:54.880 --> 32:56.000
Even without you,

32:56.350 --> 32:57.680
we still have ourselves.

32:57.680 --> 32:59.830
-Right, we have so many people here.
-We have brothers.

32:59.830 --> 33:02.240
-We must cooperate. Win the championship.
-Win the championship.

33:02.240 --> 33:03.350
We have nothing to fear!

33:03.350 --> 33:03.720
Exactly.

33:03.720 --> 33:05.030
-Yeah.
-We'll play even without Coach.

33:05.030 --> 33:07.000
-Yeah.
-Everyone is so determined?

33:07.000 --> 33:08.270
Then let's keep playing

33:08.270 --> 33:09.110
and win the championship together!

33:09.110 --> 33:10.070
-Yeah!
-Yeah!

33:10.070 --> 33:12.530
-Play until the end!
-Win the championship!

33:15.400 --> 33:17.400
-Goodbye, Coach.
-Bye-bye, coach.

33:18.790 --> 33:20.160
-Ms. Lin.
-Bye-bye.

33:20.750 --> 33:22.110
Ms. Lin is gone.

33:22.480 --> 33:23.160
There she is.

33:23.160 --> 33:26.240
-Bye-bye, Ms. Lin!
-Bye-bye, Ms. Lin!

33:26.240 --> 33:27.730
Let's go. Let's go.

33:27.750 --> 33:29.750
Let's go. Let's go.

33:51.550 --> 33:52.480
Are you tired?

33:54.550 --> 33:55.510
I'm fine.

34:08.630 --> 34:10.690
I'm not going to be a slacker anymore.

34:15.070 --> 34:15.880
I can tell.

34:18.360 --> 34:19.800
Although

34:20.150 --> 34:21.550
I don't want you to leave,

34:22.800 --> 34:25.010
whether you stay or go,

34:25.230 --> 34:26.570
I've decided

34:26.600 --> 34:27.969
to lead them

34:28.150 --> 34:29.710
to keep playing.

34:38.630 --> 34:39.800
Why are you so quiet?

34:42.760 --> 34:46.550
Are you scared
by the awakening of a slacker?

35:03.480 --> 35:04.810
Then good luck, Ms. Lin.

35:05.230 --> 35:06.890
Help them get into the top 500.

35:06.980 --> 35:08.150
Yeah.

35:10.670 --> 35:12.550
P-U-P. Am I right?

35:14.550 --> 35:16.710
Class is starting, everyone.

35:17.360 --> 35:18.630
Class is starting.

35:19.400 --> 35:20.340
Hurry up.

35:20.420 --> 35:21.360
Your turn.

35:21.980 --> 35:24.920
[Yuanyuan Tutoring Class]

35:22.360 --> 35:23.840
Now you'll behave.

35:23.840 --> 35:26.000
-Put it here.
-That's not right.

35:36.590 --> 35:38.190
Why are you such a hypocrite?

35:38.510 --> 35:40.510
Didn't someone say they were too good

35:40.510 --> 35:42.170
to study with us bad students?

35:43.700 --> 35:44.780
Grandpa's wisdom

35:44.840 --> 35:46.360
is beyond the grandkids' understanding.

35:46.360 --> 35:47.720
-I...
-Don't respond.

35:47.750 --> 35:49.840
If you do,
you'll really become his grandson.

35:49.840 --> 35:50.550
Boss!

35:51.070 --> 35:52.400
Boss, the sausages are sold out.

35:52.400 --> 35:53.800
I got you a family bucket.

35:54.840 --> 35:55.840
Hello, Ms. Lin.

35:56.440 --> 35:57.710
Thank you, Lin Lu.

35:57.710 --> 36:00.400
You're the first to notice I'm here.

36:00.880 --> 36:02.010
-Hello, Ms. Lin.
-Hello, Ms. Lin.

36:02.010 --> 36:02.730
Hello, Ms. Lin.

36:02.730 --> 36:03.920
Hello, Ms. Lin.

36:04.840 --> 36:06.100
Let's start the class.

36:13.560 --> 36:14.720
You should all know

36:14.750 --> 36:16.320
what today's topic is, right?

36:16.320 --> 36:17.720
Getting into the top 500.

36:18.320 --> 36:19.320
That's right.

36:19.320 --> 36:21.110
But among everyone here, it seems

36:21.110 --> 36:23.710
only 4 students
don't have to worry about doing that.

36:23.710 --> 36:25.920
Come on, Ms. Lin, stop saying this.

36:25.920 --> 36:27.320
Hurry up and teach us your ultimate move.

36:27.320 --> 36:28.320
My ultimate move?

36:29.000 --> 36:30.550
Unfortunately, I don't have one.

36:30.550 --> 36:31.710
We have to take it slowly.

36:31.710 --> 36:32.960
No way. How is that possible?

36:32.960 --> 36:35.400
Didn't you just help Fu beat Wen Chengye?

36:35.670 --> 36:37.110
-Right.
-Right.

36:37.590 --> 36:39.360
May I ask, dear Qin Ao,

36:39.360 --> 36:40.800
in the last English exam,

36:40.800 --> 36:42.630
how much did your score improve?

36:43.400 --> 36:44.440
Ms. Lin,

36:44.440 --> 36:46.960
Qin Ao improved a lot.

36:46.960 --> 36:48.960
He went from single digits
to double digits.

36:48.960 --> 36:50.150
Thirteen points.

36:50.880 --> 36:51.920
You talk too much!

36:52.320 --> 36:53.480
Come on, hit me!

36:54.760 --> 36:56.360
Fu Xinshu was able to improve

36:56.360 --> 36:58.710
because he already had a foundation
in grammar.

36:58.710 --> 37:00.110
I did some rough calculations.

37:00.110 --> 37:01.630
If all of you want to get into

37:01.630 --> 37:02.960
the top 500 of the grade,

37:02.960 --> 37:04.280
the average score needs to increase

37:04.280 --> 37:06.230
by about 45.67 points.

37:06.230 --> 37:08.490
Just memorizing vocabulary won't work.

37:09.190 --> 37:10.670
Six and seven?

37:10.670 --> 37:12.440
They are ominous numbers. Bad luck.

37:12.440 --> 37:14.150
-How is it bad luck?
-Shut up!

37:14.150 --> 37:14.800
Alright.

37:14.800 --> 37:16.670
Let's start our first class.

37:16.670 --> 37:18.630
First, pick a book.

37:18.630 --> 37:19.710
Any genre is fine.

37:19.710 --> 37:20.880
Any book is fine?

37:27.230 --> 37:27.840
I want this. I want this.

37:27.840 --> 37:28.840
Wen Chengye,

37:28.840 --> 37:30.170
you have to pick one too.

37:30.320 --> 37:31.920
Chen Jianghe. Chen Jianghe.

37:43.920 --> 37:44.840
Has everyone finished picking?

37:44.840 --> 37:46.030
Yes.

37:46.030 --> 37:48.360
I'll give you 40 minutes
for the first class.

37:48.360 --> 37:49.920
Read the book you chose

37:49.920 --> 37:51.400
up to page 100.

37:51.800 --> 37:52.760
After reading,

37:52.760 --> 37:54.760
take 10 minutes to give an oral summary

37:54.760 --> 37:56.230
of the content.

37:56.230 --> 37:57.230
Those who can't do it

37:57.230 --> 37:58.880
will write a 500-word book report.

37:58.880 --> 37:59.960
Wait, Ms. Lin,

37:59.960 --> 38:01.320
can I change my book?

38:01.320 --> 38:03.920
-Bro.
-100 pages is easy.

38:03.920 --> 38:05.400
But you picked a comic book.

38:05.400 --> 38:07.860
That's cheating, Ms. Lin.
It doesn't count.

38:08.360 --> 38:09.320
Change it.

38:09.320 --> 38:10.190
Look at his.

38:11.440 --> 38:12.710
Oral history?

38:12.710 --> 38:13.800
Chen Jianghe, what book did you pick?

38:13.800 --> 38:15.600
Five Thousand Years of History.

38:37.590 --> 38:39.070
Why didn't you tell me
the road was so narrow?

38:39.070 --> 38:40.440
Cars can't even get in.

38:40.440 --> 38:41.590
I had to ride an electric bike.

38:41.590 --> 38:43.000
I'm really speechless.

38:45.150 --> 38:46.360
The brother-in-law persona is set!

38:46.360 --> 38:47.130
Here.

38:47.320 --> 38:49.650
I brought them all from Yongchuan for you.

38:49.670 --> 38:51.590
Put in a good word for me
with your sister.

38:51.590 --> 38:52.480
Cut it out.

38:53.070 --> 38:54.810
You copied these yourself.

38:54.830 --> 38:56.120
I once told you to give me some,
but you refused.

38:56.120 --> 38:57.590
Why are you being so generous now?

38:57.230 --> 38:59.330
[Liverpool vs. Inter Milan]

38:59.560 --> 39:01.150
I'll show them some classic cases

39:01.150 --> 39:02.210
to help them learn.

39:03.760 --> 39:04.590
You promised

39:05.000 --> 39:07.400
to say good things about me
to your sister.

39:07.630 --> 39:08.630
I didn't say that.

39:15.210 --> 39:15.990
[Wang Tian]

39:17.800 --> 39:18.320
Hang up.

39:20.710 --> 39:22.440
Hi, Tian, it's Felix Yu.

39:23.070 --> 39:24.030
Yes, it's his fault.

39:24.030 --> 39:24.840
I'll put you on speaker now.

39:24.840 --> 39:25.760
Wait a moment.

39:26.840 --> 39:29.190
Don't you dare ignore my calls again.

39:30.320 --> 39:31.960
Anyway, you have a professional lackey

39:31.960 --> 39:33.320
reporting to you at all times.

39:33.320 --> 39:34.280
Cut the crap.

39:34.800 --> 39:35.880
I have a meeting soon.

39:35.880 --> 39:37.030
I'll just ask you this:

39:37.030 --> 39:38.760
when are you coming to Hengjiu?

39:39.030 --> 39:40.030
You finally admitted that you

39:40.030 --> 39:42.190
were the one who arranged for that person
from Hengjiu?

39:42.190 --> 39:44.030
Seriously, I don't understand.

39:44.030 --> 39:46.070
What exactly are you trying to do
by staying in Hongjing?

39:46.070 --> 39:47.840
Felix Yu said the matter
you were investigating

39:47.840 --> 39:49.070
is already over.

39:50.880 --> 39:51.630
Tian,

39:52.380 --> 39:53.920
I already agreed to be their coach.

39:53.920 --> 39:55.760
I have to teach them some real stuff.

39:55.760 --> 39:57.560
Have some professional ethics.

39:58.360 --> 39:59.280
Could it be

39:59.280 --> 40:01.480
that you are interested in that Ms. Lin?

40:01.840 --> 40:03.440
That wouldn't be a bad thing.

40:09.920 --> 40:11.520
Even your sister could tell.

40:11.920 --> 40:13.190
Stop acting deep.

40:14.400 --> 40:16.400
It's about history.

40:16.400 --> 40:18.000
It covers the period from

40:18.000 --> 40:21.760
the Three Sovereigns and Five Emperors
to the... Spring and Autumn Period, and...

40:21.760 --> 40:24.480
The interesting parts are...

40:25.070 --> 40:26.840
Coach Wang Fa is here. I give up.

40:29.670 --> 40:30.360
Hello, Coach.

40:30.360 --> 40:31.430
-Hello, Coach.
-Hello, Coach.

40:31.430 --> 40:32.590
Hello, Coach.

40:32.590 --> 40:34.720
Ms. Lin, have you finished your class?

40:35.760 --> 40:38.920
Wen Chengye and Chen Jianghe
didn't finish the summary.

40:38.920 --> 40:40.440
Write a 500-word reading report.

40:40.440 --> 40:41.920
From now on, every week,

40:41.920 --> 40:44.030
we will do this kind of reading practice
3 times.

40:44.030 --> 40:45.510
I... I don't care anyway.

40:45.510 --> 40:46.530
I'm not the only one being punished.

40:46.530 --> 40:48.860
Next time I must change to an easier book.

40:59.150 --> 41:00.000
Five?

41:01.960 --> 41:04.040
She means you two
are switching shifts.

41:04.040 --> 41:05.170
I'll high-five you.

41:07.670 --> 41:08.550
I'm leaving.

41:13.320 --> 41:14.440
First of all,

41:15.000 --> 41:18.070
congratulations on entering
the 2nd phase of the points race.

41:18.070 --> 41:19.350
The draw results

41:19.370 --> 41:20.900
will be announced in a week.

41:22.070 --> 41:23.190
If in a week,

41:23.190 --> 41:24.510
we don't even have a coach,

41:24.510 --> 41:25.710
the results won't matter.

41:25.710 --> 41:27.510
Can you shut your jinxed mouth?

41:28.360 --> 41:29.030
Coach,

41:29.030 --> 41:30.110
are you going to introduce

41:30.110 --> 41:31.230
the opponents we are about to face?

41:31.230 --> 41:32.030
Yes.

41:32.710 --> 41:33.510
But before that,

41:33.510 --> 41:34.710
I want to hear

41:35.230 --> 41:36.840
how you see yourselves now.

41:40.360 --> 41:41.480
Brothers,

41:41.480 --> 41:43.710
Coach is asking how we see ourselves.

41:43.710 --> 41:45.070
Let's show him!

41:45.070 --> 41:45.920
Come on!

41:46.670 --> 41:48.400
You even brought this back?

41:53.320 --> 41:54.320
Although

41:54.320 --> 41:55.590
Jin Laoyao

41:55.590 --> 41:57.230
won't let us hang this banner in school,

41:57.230 --> 42:00.230
the whole school already knows that

42:00.230 --> 42:01.880
the Hongjing No. 8 High School football team

42:01.880 --> 42:04.540
entered the next round
with a complete victory.

42:05.320 --> 42:06.630
It is a...

42:06.630 --> 42:09.920
-racing...
-Rising, Boss.

42:14.550 --> 42:15.510
I know.

42:17.230 --> 42:21.030
It is a rising star team!

42:22.030 --> 42:22.760
Yes.

42:23.710 --> 42:24.440
Sit down.

42:25.590 --> 42:26.810
[Hongjing No. 8 High School Football Team
Crushes Lyujing International]

42:27.030 --> 42:28.360
Ms. Lin, what about you?

42:28.840 --> 42:30.000
What do you think?

42:31.630 --> 42:34.440
The "rising star" part

42:34.440 --> 42:35.710
is quite objective.

42:36.760 --> 42:37.940
Good.

42:38.070 --> 42:40.750
Let's watch two classic matches.

42:40.840 --> 42:42.070
Put the banner away.

42:44.070 --> 42:46.550
Let's see how some classic tactics
are executed

42:46.550 --> 42:49.080
at the top level
when facing different teams.

42:49.920 --> 42:52.000
Classic matches can be reproduced,

42:52.000 --> 42:54.360
or even surpassed, by understanding,

42:53.970 --> 42:54.500
[2021 UEFA Champions League]

42:54.360 --> 42:55.480
dismantling, and careful preparation.

42:54.530 --> 42:54.990
[Chelsea vs Juventus]

42:56.190 --> 42:58.070
In the match you are watching now,

42:59.030 --> 43:01.150
their players took a total of

43:01.150 --> 43:02.480
21 shots

43:02.480 --> 43:03.540
and scored 4 goals.

43:04.110 --> 43:06.230
Their scoring efficiency is 19%.

43:07.000 --> 43:08.590
Actually,
the opponent's defensive strategy

43:08.590 --> 43:09.740
was already very good.

43:09.740 --> 43:11.070
What I hope you can learn from this

43:11.070 --> 43:13.030
is how to improve your scoring efficiency

43:13.030 --> 43:13.670
when facing

43:13.670 --> 43:15.530
this kind of defensive strategy.

43:16.350 --> 43:17.710
Good ball. The ball was passed over.

43:17.710 --> 43:19.480
Passed. They played a one-two.

43:20.360 --> 43:21.030
Pass it.

43:21.440 --> 43:23.190
This is a cutback attack.

43:24.190 --> 43:26.050
-Look at this long pass.
-Indeed.

43:29.800 --> 43:30.440
Beautiful!

43:30.440 --> 43:31.840
Good shot! This guy is...

43:32.590 --> 43:34.790
But I think there's some luck involved.

43:35.440 --> 43:37.840
-He passed the ball.
-He played it forward.

43:37.840 --> 43:38.630
A one-two.

43:38.840 --> 43:39.710
Pass.

43:40.030 --> 43:40.670
Too fast.

43:41.230 --> 43:42.510
He passed it.

43:43.670 --> 43:45.800
He just passed the ball straight away.

44:01.550 --> 44:02.590
During class today,

44:02.590 --> 44:04.920
Wen Chengye was zoning out the whole time.

44:06.360 --> 44:07.920
It was the same in reading class.

44:07.920 --> 44:10.180
I feel like he's still resisting inside.

44:14.630 --> 44:15.440
Oh no.

44:15.440 --> 44:16.510
The weather forecast today

44:16.510 --> 44:18.310
said there'd be thunderstorms!

44:25.440 --> 44:28.110
Ms. Lin, you really picked a great time
to put your books out in the sun.

44:28.110 --> 44:29.230
I put them out the day before yesterday

44:29.230 --> 44:30.710
and forgot to bring them in.

44:30.710 --> 44:31.670
Great.

44:31.670 --> 44:32.670
Very Lin Wanxing.

44:36.670 --> 44:37.670
Why do you think

44:37.670 --> 44:39.280
Wen Chengye still came even though

44:39.280 --> 44:40.680
he was so uncomfortable?

44:50.230 --> 44:53.030
What are you doing?
You almost fell down, you know?

44:55.070 --> 44:56.550
The wind is too strong.

44:57.110 --> 44:58.000
I

44:58.670 --> 45:00.480
couldn't see clearly.

45:13.800 --> 45:14.960
My hair is stuck.

45:15.840 --> 45:17.570
Go get some scissors and cut...

45:20.080 --> 45:25.580
♪ Waiting for a dark cloud
to pass by you ♪

45:23.760 --> 45:25.020
It might hurt a little.

45:26.190 --> 45:30.720
♪ Listen closely to its cries ♪

45:32.560 --> 45:37.600
♪ The heavy rain will wash away
your reflection ♪

45:38.460 --> 45:44.060
♪ And carry it toward distant scenery ♪

45:39.800 --> 45:41.400
It's because his heart

45:42.030 --> 45:43.230
is already here.

45:45.480 --> 45:51.140
♪ Every experience has its meaning ♪

45:52.080 --> 45:56.850
♪ Scene by scene, they come together
to form who I am ♪

45:58.510 --> 46:03.890
♪ Even the wounds
that leave behind their marks ♪

46:04.820 --> 46:06.150
♪ Have taught me ♪
